<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>frḥẗ wfrḥẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- frḥẗ wfrḥẗ btmlạ ḥyạty kl ṭryqy fyh ạ̉frạḥ
 frḥ kẖlạṣy wfrḥ njạty m ạlʿbwdyẗ bqyt mrtạḥ
 frḥẗ hnyẗ bạlḥryẗ frḥẗ tdwm kl ạlạ̉yạm
 frḥẗ thwn ly ạlbryẗ mhmạ ykwn fy ṭryqy ậlạm
 2- frḥẗ wfrḥẗ fy kl ṭryqy kly sʿạdẗ wạ̉nạ wyạk
 mạsk ạ̹ydy fyʿly̱ nsẖydy mạ ạ̉ḥlạhạ ạ̉yạmy mʿạk
 frḥẗ hnyẗ wạ̉ḥly̱ hdyẗ ạ̹n ḥbyby mʿạyạ ṣdyq
 frḥẗ thwn ly ạlbryẗ mhmạ ạ̉mr fy ḍʿf wḍyq
 3- frḥẗ wfrḥẗ fwq ạlạ̉frạḥ frḥty ạ̹n fy hạlqạk
 dy btrfʿny wtsẖjʿny ạ̉qḍy ḥyạty bạstnạk
 frḥẗ hnyẗ ḥạlạaⁿ jạyẗ frḥẗ hạtkml ywm lqyạk
 frḥẗ thwn ly ạlbryẗ ạ̹ny qryb hạlqạk fy smạk</lyrics>
